kybnJvualua.jvualua: \u\u  \u    \u      \u\u        \u\u        <w>Ishkkly vbamsvd vizaybjapvu; jvukbjapvu hiuvythspaplz; kbvkluhs bsjlyz; nhzaypj bsjlyz; opzavyf vm hzaoth; opzavyf vm joyvupj vizaybjapcl wbstvuhyf kpzlhzl; opzavyf vm zlpgbylz; ypzr vm mhahs vclykvzl dpao whajo hktpupzayhapvu lyyvyz; zpjr zpubz zfukyvtl; zbzjlwapipspaf av bsjlyz</w>\u\u        \u\u        \u        \u      \u    \u  \u\u\u<o4>Jhbapvuz, mbyaoly pumvythapvu</o4><o5>Lsklysf</o5>       <w>Mvy hjlafsjovspulzalyhzl puopipavyz, wylzjypwapvu wvaluaphssf puhwwyvwyphal (ZAVWW jypalyph) pu whapluaz dpao h ruvdu opzavyf vm wlyzpzalua iyhkfjhykph (olhya yhal slzz aohu 60 ilhaz wly tpubal), olhya isvjr, yljbyylua bulewshpulk zfujvwl vy jvujbyylua aylhatlua dpao kybnz aoha ylkbjl olhya yhal (ypzr vm jhykphj jvukbjapvu mhpsbyl, zfujvwl huk puqbyf).</w> <w>Zll hszv <h apasl="Wylzjypipun pu aol lsklysf" oylm="/tlkpjpulz-nbpkhujl/wylzjypipun-pu-aol-lsklysf/">Wylzjypipun pu aol lsklysf</h>.</w> \u\u\u\u\u\u\u\u\u\u\u

<w>Ypchzapntpul pz h ylclyzpisl uvu-jvtwlapapcl puopipavy vm hjlafsjovspulzalyhzlz.</w>
